_sText:
Helo. This is a short strafe map (~15 sec). If you like the bonus level of bhop_muchfast and bhop_andromeda you'll probably like this too! :)

- Lamps on bottom level of the map works as boosters. Hence why there is no trigger_teleport under pads/blocks.

- There are markings on the ground for zones. Normal & bonus.

- Map is possible with legit style.


Thanks to Noctali, RIKYY and StraY for testing and optimization.
